    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/1e29ab4439c6873fbc68b92d2ff083b1.webp?t=1767475629\" width=452 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/59cbc1148a67f023ceb88202af037d90.poster.avif?t=1767475629\" width=622 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/59cbc1148a67f023ceb88202af037d90.webm?t=1767475629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿着你的六面骰子进入90年代梦幻肉鸽游戏。用解锁的设备创造疯狂的协同效应。一场游戏时长30分钟。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/740e94fa43feef3e46b08e0a2235648b.webp?t=1767475629\" width=452 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/d93e982bd041f9f94e18bb7388cb29b7.poster.avif?t=1767475629\" width=622 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/d93e982bd041f9f94e18bb7388cb29b7.webm?t=1767475629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造 <strong>离谱连击</strong> 去破坏游戏规则, 每次醒来都<strong>解锁新</strong>的东西</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用四个能玩的人物种类去打败梦中的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁超过150个设备卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30个回忆会让你的游戏更简单。。。或奇怪</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60个不同的升级零食</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场游戏时长30分钟。尝试不同的协同效应</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[/list]</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/a21c635e10c197bc4999f95375a9319c.webp?t=1767475629\" width=452 height=46 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用90年代怀旧的小物装饰你的房间。复古的游戏，精彩的电影海报，酷炫的滑板。你需要存活千禧年的一切在你指尖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/f378bfb669f23629d2e939643998d1dc.poster.avif?t=1767475629\" width=622 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325390/extras/f378bfb669f23629d2e939643998d1dc.webm?t=1767475629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
